        <Label Content="1.   Choose &quot;From unit&quot; of measure&#xD;&#xA;2.   Choose &quot;To scale&quot;&#xD;&#xA;3.   Choose &quot;To unit&quot; of measure&#xD;&#xA;4.   Enter the size to  be calculated:&#xD;&#xA;5.   Push them calculate butten.&#xD;&#xA;" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Height="115" Margin="50,370,0,0" VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="263" FontSize="16"/>
